{"tid":1283680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭隨時被補必睇！黑警用既心理手法！","createTime":"2019-07-04T01:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:34:01.000Z","uid":26846,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"392e752d147d18ea2c453008aebe3038b1433b06","tid":1283680,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:23:03.000Z","msg":"雖然成套野並唔係最適合依家個情況，但個內容我認為幾岩大家睇！<br />\n因為文字始終唔夠畫面咁令你設身處地去明白黑警用既'套路'(諗唔倒廣東話係點形容)。<br />\n依套野講解左囚徒困境（英語：Prisoner's Dilemma），點樣令你地不攻自破！<br />\n簡單黎講就係黑警點樣套你地口供，令本來無罪既你地，變成自認有罪！<br />\n1.話有人出賣左你，你認左會減刑。<br />\n2.動之以情，叫你唔想害人就自首！<br />\n3.扮知道晒你成個作案過程，等你以為無得打，就認罪！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bXH4ldYHvCg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbXH4ldYHvCg&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0Owy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=21b452d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bXH4ldYHvCg</a><br />\n記住，當時面對既所有野都係心理手法，你只要需要記得4個字，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我無野講！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f972e251513af897111ea5df0b79b14e0cb1d5bb","tid":1283680,"uid":168485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:25:30.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"18c89fdc761d819c73ded6ba28f47080df6040cb","tid":1283680,"uid":26846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"05d62db57424c8ca116ba23ea9494a2a488dfe20","tid":1283680,"uid":256783,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"如果不斷情緒激動講「我無野講」<br />\n可唔可以要求見精神科醫生 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4cbef7ec45663d046092a3a16f2dcc5e81d3ba","tid":1283680,"uid":256783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:33:13.000Z","msg":"黑驚入唔罪又迫到我有精神病<br />\n可唔可反告返黑驚 ?"},{"pid":"16d1fa188d15ba66c3933699d5069320e646576d","tid":1283680,"uid":26846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-